        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Reef Safe Act of 2021 </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Food and Drug Administration(FDA) to develop labeling criteria and standards for <i></i><i>Reef Safe</i> and <em>Ocean Safe </em>designations on nonprescription sunscreen. The FDA must also review (and revise if necessary) the criteria and standards for such designations at least once every 10 years. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
